Title: Screening Currents Ward Identity and Integral Formulas for the WZNW

Correlation FunctionsAuthors: Hidetoshi Awata

Comments: 26 pages

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys.Suppl. 110 (1992) 303-320

We derive, based on the Wakimoto realization, the integral formulas for theWZNW correlation functions. The role of the ``screening currents Wardidentity'' is demonstrated with explicit examples. We also give a more simpleproof of a previous result.